      "content": "i cant even sleep anymore. every time i close my eyes i just keep thinking about the climate data and the feedback loops and the fact that everything is basically already broken. like what is even the point of trying to build a life or a career or anything when the world is just a house on fire? it feels so pointless to even exist in a timeline that's clearly dying.",
